{"tid":1241924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（奉勸）係呢個愈黎愈失敗主義既氣氛下，大家睇住自己朋友","createTime":"2019-06-19T01:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T01:47:18.000Z","uid":143343,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d7fd40431391eba56869e0bffb1599ea119325d","tid":1241924,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:21:13.000Z","msg":"我先唔理遊行人數，但係呢個氣氛下，真係要睇住自己啲朋友<br />\n<br />\n因為我身邊有啲人已經出現無力感，但同平時唔同既係佢地唔係選擇善忘繼續番學，係想選擇捨棄自己既生命提醒香港人唔可以就咁完左呢場運動，我開解緊佢<br />\n<br />\n我唔知連登啲朋友多唔多係咁，但呢次同平時既善忘唔太一樣 ，都係個句係呢個氣氛下，真係要睇住自己啲朋友"},{"pid":"70addc3d5b5843ac4d0e7fd1aa5b8e6b544ab256","tid":1241924,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:22:07.000Z","msg":"希望有巴打見到"},{"pid":"7703aa0440fdc6f8c282fc92216abbe20572ed43","tid":1241924,"uid":94834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少"},{"pid":"5f1a7aa4773c4c79e343082cc099823a239e0a0f","tid":1241924,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7703aa0440fdc6f8c282fc92216abbe20572ed43","tid":1241924,"uid":94834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"一個都不能少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:24:30.000Z","msg":"我唔想遊行人數尾數變 02。03 <br />\n<br />\n大家加油贏呢場杖"},{"pid":"db6d4fe4e719b4c9f09f2b731a6b789835af3429","tid":1241924,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:30:44.000Z","msg":"頂住啊大家"},{"pid":"a7c4cb3dba7a66c7eebb35f89eaddcf5a0bd051d","tid":1241924,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6001f2f86c8ae0bc0002a3e5869b8db53da1e6b7","tid":1241924,"uid":247482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:43:28.000Z","msg":"終於明白情緒病既人有幾痛苦<br />\n果種無力感同絕望揮之不去，就算明知咁樣無補於事，但真係控制唔到<br />\n<br />\n自問承受能力/抗壓力都算唔差<br />\n大家真係要睇住身邊朋友，有異樣即刻的佢睇醫生"},{"pid":"046072ac09b357d64b7fda6a31fdbca1a3238c48","tid":1241924,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:44:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9b6f503dc18d08875b2e7895ee4079e0a0ad3ee","tid":1241924,"uid":173814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"其實無需要失敗主義，因為件事情都未完，仲有620，G20，71等事可以扭轉情勢，點會咁易放棄"}]}